{"type": "article", "id": 9403, "title": "BigStuffed 大型布艺玩偶", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-11T07:22:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235240sdTODozEYj6KGvUh.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t现居巴黎的以色列时装设计师 Dana Muskat 试图为自己哥哥的女儿做一个独特的出生礼物，于是她做了一个大型的布艺玩偶，守护小侄女的降生。而设计师渐渐意识到，这种玩偶被各个年龄段的人喜爱，于是诞生了 “BigStuffed” 这个项目诞生。这些玩偶的原型都由 Dana Muskat 亲自设计，简单可爱，材料上采用天然的棉花和羊毛，颜色上以柔软温和的色调为主，带来满满的温暖和爱意。这些玩偶<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/BigStuffed\" target=\"_blank\">在这里可以买到</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235235B5gX8kl3wd7sMKQI.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235235mYb4cGPjZ813qyvp.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052352360bSQyTPYl3j7zk8H.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523523629R5zpWZlMqiI0xV.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235237nRvFS0xGufAyp9tb.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.65520833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235237zQXjO3WowHLqsJ7l.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.615625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523523852eWK9rmv1EMAslO.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235238q4SxgCprb6QhTFXf.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.49166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235239i7EoqBaxWJhKU48Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-rat